  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the City</strong><br>Roam freely in a large city, discovering parks, streets, and new places through public transport. Every corner invites you to a new adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/9ca252acc67e4936ddfda90a523d4e7c.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/9ca252acc67e4936ddfda90a523d4e7c.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create Your Own Style</strong><br>Choose your style from clothing stores, shape your hair and beard at the barber, and stay fit at the gym. Create a unique look for yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/163293b9f13b08aeacee56f599dd3f04.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/163293b9f13b08aeacee56f599dd3f04.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/48e5a4a89488b7e2c29bcfde16246f3e.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/48e5a4a89488b7e2c29bcfde16246f3e.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/38b4ddf7f26d8b8e86f0dd0762dcf8fd.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/38b4ddf7f26d8b8e86f0dd0762dcf8fd.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Luxurious Life</strong><br>As you grow wealthier, build the luxurious lifestyle you've dreamed of. Elevate your living standard with stylish cars and luxury homes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/6a7a92002484ecefc9285e2ed99c482c.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/6a7a92002484ecefc9285e2ed99c482c.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Social Life</strong><br>Meet women, party at nightclubs, and embrace new experiences in your social life.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/e0eb41c1f07f4fb0e4971b5eb6b8d4d6.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/e0eb41c1f07f4fb0e4971b5eb6b8d4d6.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/b26e2f87500f218edfdd8c9da8c41ef1.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/b26e2f87500f218edfdd8c9da8c41ef1.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various Job Opportunities</strong><br>Earn money by working different jobs. Become a bus driver, waiter, or supermarket employee while exploring the city.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/2064a25862bba945a269375322ed511d.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/2064a25862bba945a269375322ed511d.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/b0142ecf3847ed3f3ac55c247274bc9c.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/b0142ecf3847ed3f3ac55c247274bc9c.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/c16f35fc0c1f80f2c0b1aee010dc7e66.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/c16f35fc0c1f80f2c0b1aee010dc7e66.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><br> </p></li></ul>",
